-This patch makes samba_cross.py compatible with old bash (e.g. 3.2)
-
-Signed-off-by: Sergey V. Lobanov <sergey@lobanov.in>
-Reviewed-by: Christof Schmitt <cs@samba.org>
-Reviewed-by: Andreas Schneider <asn@samba.org>
